<p>The code point index of the first code point in the cluster that the
point is closest to.</p>


<pre class="language-csharp"><code class="language-csharp">public int ClosestCodePointIndex;</code></pre>

<h2 id="remarks">Remarks</h2><p>If the point is over a cluster, the returned code point index will vary
depending whether the point is in the left or right half of the cluster
and the text direction of that cluster.</p>
<p>This value represents the code point index that the caret should be moved to
if the user clicked the mouse at this position.  To determine the co-ordinates
and shape of the caret, see <a href="./../caret">Caret Information</a>.</p>

